Emergency Drone Simulation System
├── Simulation Environment
│   ├── 3D Terrain & Infrastructure Models
│   ├── Weather & Environmental Conditions
│   ├── Dynamic Events (e.g., fire spread, flooding)
│   └── Human Behavior Modeling
│
├── Drone Subsystem
│   ├── UAV Models
│   │   ├── Fixed-wing
│   │   └── Multirotor
│   ├── Sensor Suite
│   │   ├── Camera (RGB, IR)
│   │   ├── LiDAR
│   │   ├── GPS/IMU
│   │   └── Gas/Environmental Sensors
│   ├── Communication Module
│   └── Flight Control System
│
├── AI & Decision Support
│   ├── Path Planning Algorithms
│   ├── Obstacle Avoidance
│   ├── Target Detection & Recognition
│   ├── Mission Planning & Optimization
│   └── Human-Drone Interaction Logic
│
├── User Interface & Visualization
│   ├── Control Dashboard
│   ├── Real-time Monitoring
│   ├── VR/AR Interfaces
│   └── Data Playback & Analysis Tools
│
└── Performance Evaluation & Analytics
    ├── Response Time Metrics
    ├── Resource Utilization
    ├── Accuracy of Detection/Delivery
    ├── Simulation Logging & Reporting
    └── Scenario Outcome Analysis
